      "requiredLevel": 1,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "Iterative solver residuals monitored to convergence tolerance of 1e-6 for all load steps. Newton-Raphson iteration converged within 8 iterations per step for all 11 constructs. No spurious energy growth detected."
    },
    {
