      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "Simulation protocols reviewed by independent analyst; boundary condition application and material assignment cross-checked against test setup documentation. Standardised input decks with locked parameter ranges prevent inadvertent user modification."
