      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "Linear elastic constitutive model with Ti-6Al-4V material properties is appropriate for the sub-yield loading regime of the ASTM F1717 protocol. Contact between screw head and rod modelled with penalty formulation validated against closed-form solutions."
    },
    {
