      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "Material properties sourced from ASTM F136 coupon data for each lot; geometric dimensions measured via CMM on three representative screws per construct. Torque preload on set screw converted to equivalent clamping force using calibrated torque-tension relationship."
    },
