      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "N=11 constructs drawn from production lots; sample size provides adequate statistical basis for mean and variability characterisation at the Medium assurance level. Dimensional inspection confirms constructs fall within design tolerances."
