      "rationale": "Testing conducted under a single load angle (5-degree compression-bending) per ASTM F1717. Required level 3 calls for multiple load conditions spanning the clinical envelope; only one condition tested. Shortfall acknowledged; sponsor has accepted residual uncertainty given the conservative nature of the single-condition test."
