      "rationale": "Quantitative validation metric (E_rms normalised by experimental mean) computed for construct stiffness and peak load at 5 mm displacement. All three FEA codes yield E_rms below 10% threshold. Prediction intervals overlap experimental scatter bands for all 11 constructs."
