    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Overall credibility assessment outcome is Accepted at Medium assurance level. Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 factors meet or exceed required levels. The single shortfall in Test conditions (achieved 2, required 3) has been reviewed and risk-accepted by the device sponsor given the conservative nature of the ASTM F1717 single-condition protocol. The FEA ensemble demonstrates consistent predictive accuracy across two independent laboratories and N=11 constructs, supporting regulatory submission for the non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw construct.",
